# cc-sdlc — Full SDLC Orchestration for Claude Code

Modular plugin collection for Claude Code that spans the software development lifecycle. {{AGENT_COUNT}} specialized agents, {{SKILL_COUNT}} skills, {{COMMAND_COUNT}} commands, {{HOOK_COUNT}} hook scripts, hook-driven quality gates, complexity-based routing with configurable model tiers, and optional Agent Teams for parallel execution.

## What This Is

A collection of Claude Code plugins that orchestrate development workflows from spec through deployment:

- **{{PLUGIN_COUNT}} plugins** — core SDLC, coding standards, GitHub, Jira, Confluence, Jama
- **{{AGENT_COUNT}} specialized agents** — conductor, planner, architect, implementer, reviewer, threat-modeler, and more
- **{{SKILL_COUNT}} skills** — {{LANG_SKILL_COUNT}} language standards, {{DOMAIN_SKILL_COUNT}} domain overlays, {{CORE_SKILL_COUNT}} core workflow skills, {{INTEG_SKILL_COUNT}} integration skills
- **{{COMMAND_COUNT}} slash commands** — `/conduct`, `/plan`, `/implement`, `/review`, `/spec`, `/threat-model`, `/team`, and more
- **{{HOOK_COUNT}} hook scripts** — secret detection, bash safety, deploy guard, compliance logging, team lifecycle
- **Complexity-based routing** — INSTANT → STANDARD → DEEP → ULTRADEEP
- **3 model tiers** — Opus (judgment), Sonnet (execution), Haiku (triage)
- **Optional Agent Teams** — parallel execution for DEEP/ULTRADEEP tasks (~7x cost, opt-in)

## Quick Start

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://github.com/kennedym-ds/claudecode-orchestrator.git
cd claudecode-orchestrator

# Install core + standards to your project
bash installer/install.sh --target /path/to/your/project
# Or Windows:
pwsh -File installer/install.ps1 -TargetPath C:\path\to\project

# Install all plugins (including integrations)
bash installer/install.sh --target /path/to/your/project --plugins all

# Validate
bash scripts/validate-assets.sh

# Start working
claude --agent conductor
```

## Plugins

| Plugin | Description | Assets |
|--------|-------------|--------|
| **cc-sdlc-core** | SDLC orchestration engine | {{CORE_AGENT_COUNT}} agents, {{CORE_SKILL_COUNT}} skills, {{CORE_COMMAND_COUNT}} commands, 6 rules, {{HOOK_COUNT}} hooks |
| **cc-sdlc-standards** | Universal coding standards | {{LANG_SKILL_COUNT}} language skills + {{DOMAIN_SKILL_COUNT}} domain overlays |
| **cc-github** | GitHub integration | 2 agents, 2 commands, 2 skills + GitHub MCP |
| **cc-jira** | Jira integration | 1 agent, 2 commands, 2 skills + Jira MCP |
| **cc-confluence** | Confluence integration | 1 agent, 2 commands, 3 skills + Confluence MCP |
| **cc-jama** | Jama integration | 1 agent, 2 commands, 2 skills + Jama MCP |

Install individually: `--plugins core,github` or all: `--plugins all`

